summary: This reskins all of the wall and ground textures to make all dungeon caves feel like a sand cave.
descriptionHtml:
This is an idea I had after going through cave dungeons in Skyrim, while default looks good I had a personal taste for more sandy like caves with a brighter rocky wall to blend into it better.

All textures used here are new to skyrim, they weren\'t taken from some other folder. New fresh feel!

Check out the screen-shots and let me know what you think!
Happy Modding!
author: TheWizard200
